{"body": "The current state of this is terrible.  You should not have to jump through hoops to make the logger actually useful.  99% of the time you don't want your development logs filled up with noise from the assets being requested.  The rails server log is functionally broken as it stands.\r\n\r\nIf you want to maintain the purity of the logger, then maybe it can be monkey patched within the development environment configuration.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/13446926", "created_at": "2013-02-12T18:16:05Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3795#issuecomment-13446926", "updated_at": "2013-02-12T18:18:31Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3795, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/MarcoPeraza", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6f636cd8d89a938a0e3efc7f0bd84773?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc0d98530741a87ad5545350a279dd30c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6f636cd8d89a938a0e3efc7f0bd84773", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "MarcoPeraza", "type": "User", "id": 686719, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/MarcoPeraza/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5238317ebd3543c15100f787"}, "id": 13446926, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3795"}
